          <td>
            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2">
              <tr> 
                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Advanced Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Furry little ball of fury</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.00)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=24042">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9510">Haris "Shockwaver" Kopic</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9510&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> This deck examplifies what Naroom was intended to be like. Lots of small creatures and plenty of spells, relics, and effects to pump em.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> June 20, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Magi <br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(410)">Evu</a> <br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(403)">Plith</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(400)">Furok</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(428)">Vortex of Knowledge</a>) <br>
<br>
Chayala <br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(399)">Eebit</a>, Rabbage, <a href="javascript:card_browser(616)">Gilded Cage</a>) <br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(515)">Eidon</a> <br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(400)">Furok</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(603)">Forest Jile</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(423)">Grow</a>) <br>
<br>
Creatures: <br>
<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(399)">Eebit</a> x3 <br>
Rabbage x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(607)">Wasperine</a> x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(404)">Rudwot</a> x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(400)">Furok</a> x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(751)">Elder <a href="javascript:card_browser(409)">Weebo</a></a> x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(604}<a href="javascript:card_browser({400)">Furok</a> Guardian</a> x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(409)">Weebo</a> x3 <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(603)">Forest Jile</a> x1 <br>
